class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 15, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104job1665702916386.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/job1665702916386.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/job1665702916386.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"job1665702916386\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"job1665702916386__database_connector_requests_425613\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A database connector implements a set of generic Uniface requests for the underlying\n      DBMS. Connector requests are well-defined tasks performed by the DBMS connector when it is\n      called.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"job1665702916386__p_d129974e1_d129975e1_d129976e1\">Connector requests are recognized by every Uniface DBMS connector. Each request is identified by an alphabetic character, such as O for Open or S for Select.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"job1665702916386__p_d129977e1_d129978e1_d129979e1\">The field <code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;ufunc</code> indicates\n         the connector request that must be performed. Some connector requests have multiple modes.\n         The requested mode is available in the field <code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;umode</code> in all\n         connector requests, except the Info request. In the Info request, the mode is available in\n         the field <code class=\"ph codeph\">uinfo-&gt;umode</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Uniface Connector Requests</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\">Connector Request </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\">Value of uctrl-&gt;ufunc </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Description </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">Details </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"4\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1 job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2 job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3 job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">Connector control: </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\"> Info</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\">I</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Supply DBMS and connector characteristic.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yla1665702916470.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yla1665702916470.html\" title=\"Provide Uniface with DBMS and connector characteristics, or supply logon information.\">Info ('I')</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\"> Message</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\"> M</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Translate a connector or DBMS error code to a\n                     text.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dgv1665702916539.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dgv1665702916539.html\" title=\"Translate an error code to a text.\">Message ('M')</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"3\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1 job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2 job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Logon path control: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\">Logon</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\">L</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Log on to the DBMS.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hjv1665702916609.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hjv1665702916609.html\" title=\"Log on to the DBMS.\">Logon ('L')</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\"> Logoff</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\">A</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Log off from the DBMS. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bnm1665702916682.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bnm1665702916682.html\" title=\"Log off from the DBMS.\">Logoff ('A')</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"3\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1 job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2 job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Table control:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\">Open</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\"> O</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Open a table or create Data Definition Language\n                     (DDL) scripts to define a table and its relations.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rha1665702916756.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rha1665702916756.html\" title=\"Open or create a table, generate Data Definition Language (DDL) to create a table, or create SQL scripts to handle referential constraints.\">Open ('O')</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\"> Name table</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\"> N</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Construct the name of the overflow table. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zvk1665702916825.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zvk1665702916825.html\" title=\"Construct the name of the overflow table.\">Name table ('N')</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\"> Close</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\">Z</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Close a table.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yjg1665702916894.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yjg1665702916894.html\" title=\"Close a table.\">Close ('Z')</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"3\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1 job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2 job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Data manipulation:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\">Select</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\">S</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Select the records that match a specified\n                     profile.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kud1665702916962.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kud1665702916962.html\" title=\"Select the records from a table that match a specified profile.\">Select ('S')</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\">Fetch</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\">F</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Fetch or lock a record.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vwu1665702917038.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vwu1665702917038.html\" title=\"Fetch a record from a table or lock a record.\">Fetch ('F')</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\">Write</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\">W</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Insert a new record.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dab1665702917106.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dab1665702917106.html\" title=\"Insert a new record.\">Write ('W')</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\">Update</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\"> U</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Update an existing record.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ahd1665702917174.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ahd1665702917174.html\" title=\"Update an existing record.\">Update (U)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\">Delete</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\">D</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Delete a record.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ylh1665702917247.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ylh1665702917247.html\" title=\"Delete a record.\">Delete ('D')</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\">Wildcard delete/nullify</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\">*</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Delete or nullify a set of records. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fte1665702917323.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fte1665702917323.html\" title=\"Delete or nullify a set of records.\">Wildcard delete/nullify (*)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"3\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1 job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2 job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Transaction control: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\">Commit</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\">C</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Commit a transaction.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wfn1665702917392.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wfn1665702917392.html\" title=\"Commit the transaction on the current logon path. If the DBMS does not support Commit, return 0 to Uniface.\">Commit ('C')</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\"> Rollback</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\">R</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">Roll back a transaction.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xgp1665702917460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xgp1665702917460.html\" title=\"Roll back the transaction.\">Rollback ('R')</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\"> Global Transaction</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\">G</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\">The connector is transaction manager (TM)\n                     controlled and the kernel needs TM-specific information.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wpm1665702917532.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wpm1665702917532.html\" title=\"Provide Uniface with the DBMS-specific information that the transaction manager (TM) needs to log on to the DBMS.\">Global Transaction ('G')</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"4\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1 job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2 job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3 job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\">\n                     Miscellaneous:\n                  </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__1\">Sql</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__2\">Q</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__3\"> Submit a Data Manipulation Language (DML)\n                     statement to the DBMS.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"job1665702916386__table_d15473e1_d15474e1_d15475e1__entry__4\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"htp1665702716758.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/htp1665702716758.html\" title=\"Execute SQL statement.\">Q Sql</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/azl1665702915888.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uctrl</a><p>Exchanges general information between Uniface and the connector, and describes a table.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iga1665702915956.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uinfo</a><p>Supplies Uniface with basic information about the DBMS and the connector.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528967\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528967\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Database Connector Requests Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 15, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 A database connector implements a set of generic Uniface requests for the underlying DBMS. Connector requests are well-defined tasks performed by the DBMS connector when it is called. Connector requests are recognized by every Uniface DBMS connector. Each request is identified by an alphabetic character, such as O for Open or S for Select. The field uctrl->ufunc indicates the connector request that must be performed. Some connector requests have multiple modes. The requested mode is available in the field uctrl->umode in all connector requests, except the Info request. In the Info request, the mode is available in the field uinfo->umode . Table 1. Uniface Connector Requests Connector Request Value of uctrl->ufunc Description Details Connector control: Info I Supply DBMS and connector characteristic. Info ('I') Message M Translate a connector or DBMS error code to a text. Message ('M') Logon path control: Logon L Log on to the DBMS. Logon ('L') Logoff A Log off from the DBMS. Logoff ('A') Table control: Open O Open a table or create Data Definition Language (DDL) scripts to define a table and its relations. Open ('O') Name table N Construct the name of the overflow table. Name table ('N') Close Z Close a table. Close ('Z') Data manipulation: Select S Select the records that match a specified profile. Select ('S') Fetch F Fetch or lock a record. Fetch ('F') Write W Insert a new record. Write ('W') Update U Update an existing record. Update (U) Delete D Delete a record. Delete ('D') Wildcard delete/nullify * Delete or nullify a set of records. Wildcard delete/nullify (*) Transaction control: Commit C Commit a transaction. Commit ('C') Rollback R Roll back a transaction. Rollback ('R') Global Transaction G The connector is transaction manager (TM) controlled and the kernel needs TM-specific information. Global Transaction ('G') Miscellaneous: Sql Q Submit a Data Manipulation Language (DML) statement to the DBMS. Q Sql Related Links uctrl Exchanges general information between Uniface and the connector, and describes a table. uinfo Supplies Uniface with basic information about the DBMS and the connector. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}